title: Armbian Linux Is Now Available for Raspberry Pi 5 Computers
description:
Armbian Linux is now available for Raspberry Pi 5 computers with Debian GNU/Linux 12 "Bookworm" and Ubuntu 22.04 LTS builds featuring KDE Plasma, GNOME, Xfce, Cinnamon, and i3 graphical environments.

title: Fedora Asahi Remix Officially Released for Apple Silicon Macs
description:
Fedora Asahi Remix is now available for download as a Fedora Linux spin that runs on Apple Silicon Macs with the KDE Plasma desktop environment on Wayland.
